REMARKS BY HIS EXCELLENCY, MUHAMMADU BUHARI, PRESIDENT OF THE FEDERAL REPUBLIC OF NIGERIA, DURING HIS AUDIENCE WITH THE NATIONAL EXECUTIVE COUNCIL MEMBERS OF THE NATIONAL UNION OF PETROLEUM AND NATURAL GAS WORKERS, THURSDAY 13TH DECEMBER 2018  PROTOCOLS:  I welcome you to this gathering and thank you for your unflinching support to this administration over the last three years. I regularly receive feedback on your positive and constructive engagements with the government.               Thank you and God bless Nigeria.